title: Recap of Cowboys' MNF win & Jane Slater joins to talk Cowboys' storylines
itunes:title: Recap of Cowboys' MNF win & Jane Slater joins to talk Cowboys' storylines
description:
Jane Slater joins Daniel Jeremiah in this episode of the Move The Sticks podcast to recap the Cowboys win over the Giants on Monday Night Football (5:25), give the latest on Dak Prescott's contract situation (9:24) and to chat about her favorite Texas Longhorns (16:02)!
